#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.roc_curve.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.metrics.roc\\_curve"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:1 of
msgid "Compute Receiver operating characteristic (ROC)"
msgstr "计算接收者操作特征（ROC）"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:3 of
msgid "Note: this implementation is restricted to the binary classification task."
msgstr "注意：此实现仅限于二分类任务。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:5 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <roc_metrics>`."
msgstr "更多信息请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <roc_metrics>`。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:7 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"True binary labels. If labels are not either {-1, 1} or {0, 1}, then "
"pos_label should be explicitly given."
msgstr "真实的二分类标签。如果标签不是{-1, 1}或{0, 1}，则应显式指定pos_label。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:10 of
msgid ""
"Target scores, can either be probability estimates of the positive class,"
" confidence values, or non-thresholded measure of decisions (as returned "
"by \"decision_function\" on some classifiers)."
msgstr ""
"目标得分，可以是正类的概率估计、置信度值，或非阈值化的决策度量（例如某些"
"分类器的\"decision_function\"返回值）。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:14 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The label of the positive class. When ``pos_label=None``, if y_true is in"
" {-1, 1} or {0, 1}, ``pos_label`` is set to 1, otherwise an error will be"
" raised."
msgstr ""
"正类的标签。当 ``pos_label=None`` 时，若 y_true 属于 {-1, 1} 或 {0, 1}，"
"则 ``pos_label`` 被设为 1，否则将抛出错误。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:18 of
msgid "Sample weights."
msgstr "样本权重。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:20 of
msgid ""
"Whether to drop some suboptimal thresholds which would not appear on a "
"plotted ROC curve. This is useful in order to create lighter ROC curves."
msgstr ""
"是否丢弃一些不会出现在ROC曲线上的次优阈值。这对于生成更轻便的ROC曲线很"
"有用。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:25 of
msgid ""
"* **fpr** (*tensor, shape = [>2]*) -- Increasing false positive rates "
"such that element i is the false   positive rate of predictions with "
"score >= thresholds[i]. * **tpr** (*tensor, shape = [>2]*) -- Increasing "
"true positive rates such that element i is the true   positive rate of "
"predictions with score >= thresholds[i]. * **thresholds** (*tensor, shape"
" = [n_thresholds]*) -- Decreasing thresholds on the decision function "
"used to compute   fpr and tpr. `thresholds[0]` represents no instances "
"being predicted   and is arbitrarily set to `max(y_score) + 1`."
msgstr ""
"* **fpr** (*tensor, shape = [>2]*) -- 递增的假正率，其中元素i表示得分 >= "
"thresholds[i] 的预测的假正率。\n"
"* **tpr** (*tensor, shape = [>2]*) -- 递增的真正率，其中元素i表示得分 >= "
"thresholds[i] 的预测的真正率。\n"
"* **thresholds** (*tensor, shape = [n_thresholds]*) -- 决策函数上用于计算"
" fpr 和 tpr 的递减阈值。\n"
"`thresholds[0]` 表示没有实例被预测，该值被任意设置为 `max(y_score) + 1`。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:25 of
msgid ""
"**fpr** (*tensor, shape = [>2]*) -- Increasing false positive rates such "
"that element i is the false positive rate of predictions with score >= "
"thresholds[i]."
msgstr ""
"**fpr** (*tensor, shape = [>2]*) -- 递增的假正率，其中元素i表示得分 >= "
"thresholds[i] 的预测的假正率。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:27 of
msgid ""
"**tpr** (*tensor, shape = [>2]*) -- Increasing true positive rates such "
"that element i is the true positive rate of predictions with score >= "
"thresholds[i]."
msgstr ""
"**tpr** (*tensor, shape = [>2]*) -- 递增的真正率，其中元素i表示得分 >= "
"thresholds[i] 的预测的真正率。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:29 of
msgid ""
"**thresholds** (*tensor, shape = [n_thresholds]*) -- Decreasing "
"thresholds on the decision function used to compute fpr and tpr. "
"`thresholds[0]` represents no instances being predicted and is "
"arbitrarily set to `max(y_score) + 1`."
msgstr ""
"**thresholds** (*tensor, shape = [n_thresholds]*) -- 决策函数上用于计算 "
"fpr 和 tpr 的递减阈值。\n"
"`thresholds[0]` 表示没有实例被预测，该值被任意设置为 `max(y_score) + 1`。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`roc_auc_score`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:36 of
msgid "Compute the area under the ROC curve"
msgstr "计算ROC曲线下面积"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:39 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:40 of
msgid ""
"Since the thresholds are sorted from low to high values, they are "
"reversed upon returning them to ensure they correspond to both ``fpr`` "
"and ``tpr``, which are sorted in reversed order during their calculation."
msgstr ""
"由于阈值是按从低到高的顺序排列的，返回时会将其反转，以确保它们与 ``fpr`` "
"和 ``tpr`` 相对应，这两个值在计算过程中是按相反顺序排列的。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:45 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._ranking.roc_curve:46 of
msgid ""
